#. Tag: screen
#: libvirt_configuration.xml:1257
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"[Unit]\n"
"Before=\n"
"[Service]\n"
"Type=oneshot\n"
"RemainAfterExit=true\n"
"ExecStart=/bin/bash -c \"echo 1 > /sys/bus/pci/devices/0000:06:00.1/"
